  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Car For Sale Simulator 23 is generally a car buying and selling game. It is designed for car enthusiasts and business simulation lovers. You purchase and sell used cars from marketplaces and neighborhoods, and then expand your business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alright, hold on! Go to the car market and buy a vehicle. Repair your car, modify it as you wish, and decide whether to keep it for yourself or sell it. Earn money and grow your business to start selling more cars.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/77ee9d65070b6decadfadad5f64b5818.poster.avif?t=1774423685\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/77ee9d65070b6decadfadad5f64b5818.webm?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/77ee9d65070b6decadfadad5f64b5818.mp4?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Negotiate when buying a car. Gradually improve your bargaining skills to engage in bigger deals. Remember that the other party might try to deceive you. You can request an appraisal report or trust the other party.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/1fad9976bb682ab2387337bd69b4b252.poster.avif?t=1774423685\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/1fad9976bb682ab2387337bd69b4b252.webm?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/1fad9976bb682ab2387337bd69b4b252.mp4?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repair the cars you have purchased, modify them to your liking, paint them, and wash them. Create a top-notch car from scratch and buy it at the best price!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/d097a6bb1590dac32afd5c6c5b4f11a2.poster.avif?t=1774423685\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/d097a6bb1590dac32afd5c6c5b4f11a2.webm?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/d097a6bb1590dac32afd5c6c5b4f11a2.mp4?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your office to sell more cars. Establish the largest car dealership in your city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Some features of the game include;</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ cars and countless combinations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Car buying and selling systems with dialogue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Appraisal system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Car accident and repair system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Car painting system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Car modification system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auction system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-speed racing tracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gas and car wash systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tablet system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Banking and taxation systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill tree system</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Car For Sale Simulator 23 is generally a car buying and selling game. It is designed for car enthusiasts and business simulation lovers. You purchase and sell used cars from marketplaces and neighborhoods, and then expand your business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alright, hold on! Go to the car market and buy a vehicle. Repair your car, modify it as you wish, and decide whether to keep it for yourself or sell it. Earn money and grow your business to start selling more cars.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/77ee9d65070b6decadfadad5f64b5818.poster.avif?t=1774423685\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/77ee9d65070b6decadfadad5f64b5818.webm?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/77ee9d65070b6decadfadad5f64b5818.mp4?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Negotiate when buying a car. Gradually improve your bargaining skills to engage in bigger deals. Remember that the other party might try to deceive you. You can request an appraisal report or trust the other party.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/1fad9976bb682ab2387337bd69b4b252.poster.avif?t=1774423685\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/1fad9976bb682ab2387337bd69b4b252.webm?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/1fad9976bb682ab2387337bd69b4b252.mp4?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repair the cars you have purchased, modify them to your liking, paint them, and wash them. Create a top-notch car from scratch and buy it at the best price!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/d097a6bb1590dac32afd5c6c5b4f11a2.poster.avif?t=1774423685\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/d097a6bb1590dac32afd5c6c5b4f11a2.webm?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248760/extras/d097a6bb1590dac32afd5c6c5b4f11a2.mp4?t=1774423685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your office to sell more cars. Establish the largest car dealership in your city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Some features of the game include;</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ cars and countless combinations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Car buying and selling systems with dialogue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Appraisal system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Car accident and repair system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Car painting system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Car modification system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auction system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-speed racing tracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gas and car wash systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tablet system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Banking and taxation systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill tree system</p></li></ul>",
